OL,6,F"I didn't feel safe."
OL,8,FZaf Iqbal, from Sunderland, opened up
OL,9,Fabout how one night in August, made
OL,10,Fhim fear for his life.
OL,12,FOn 2 August, violence and disorder
OL,13,Fbroke out in Sunderland. Far-right
OL,14,Fcrowds descended onto the Anwaar e
OL,15,FMadinah mosque. Inside the mosque was
OL,16,FZaf and a few others. They had to
OL,17,Fbarricade themselves in for safety.
