OL,6,F"We could see from the windows that
OL,7,Fthe crowds were trying to push past
OL,8,Fpolice. So the fear was the crowd
OL,9,Fcould break through at any moment."
OL,11,F"And if they pushed their way through
OL,12,Fthere, I can't say what damage could
OL,13,Fhave happened (not just) to us
OL,14,Fphysically but to the building," he
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FHe added: "It was sad to see that
OL,18,Fhappen to my home city, I was born and
OL,19,Fraised here. It's not anything you
OL,20,Fexpect to see."
