OL,6,FViolent disorder flared up in
OL,7,Fdifferent parts of the UK over a week,
OL,8,Fincluding in Hartlepool, Sunderland,
OL,9,FMiddlesbrough and Darlington.
OL,11,FIt began after misinformation spread
OL,12,Fonline over the identity of a suspect
OL,13,Finvolved in a stabbing attack at a
OL,14,Fchildren's dance class in Southport,
OL,15,FMerseyside, on 29 July 2024, where
OL,16,Fthree young girls were killed.
OL,18,FIn some cities across the UK, rioters
OL,19,Fhad set fire to hotels housing asylum
OL,20,Fseekers, and launched bricks and
OL,21,Ffireworks at police.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/20
