OL,6,FFor Mohsan Ishaq, the riots that
OL,7,Fhappened over the summer still remains
OL,8,Fon his mind.
OL,10,F"It does worry me, it does worry me,
OL,11,Flike if this happened, could it happen
OL,12,Fagain? God forbid, we don't want
OL,13,Fsomething like that," he said.
OL,15,FPolling group Muslim Census surveyed
OL,16,F1,519 Muslims to see how the recent
OL,17,Friots had impacted the UK Muslim
OL,18,Fcommunity.
OL,20,F92% of respondents said they now felt
OL,21,F"much less safe."
