OL,7,Fthey had personally experienced an
OL,8,FIslamophobic or racist incident during
OL,9,Fthe week of national unrest.
OL,11,FThe disorder across the country
OL,12,Fbrought back some painful memories
OL,13,Famong British Asians living in our
OL,14,Fregion.
