OL,6,F"I had some verbal abuse and name
OL,7,Fcalling," he said.
OL,9,FAround the mid-1980s, he moved to
OL,10,FNorth Tyneside to open a corner shop.
OL,11,FIt was just a few years later that he
OL,12,Fexperienced the Meadow Well estate
OL,13,Friots.
OL,15,FUnrest broke out on a North Tyneside
OL,16,Festate on the night of 9 September
