OL,6,FThe violence was sparked after the
OL,7,Fdeaths of two joyriders, Dale Robson,
OL,8,F17, and Colin Atkins, 21. They were
OL,9,Fkilled when their stolen car went out
OL,10,Fof control while being chased by
OL,11,Fpolice at high speed.
OL,13,FRumours quickly circulated that
OL,14,Fofficers had rammed their car and
OL,15,Falthough nothing substantiated these
OL,16,Fclaims, it stirred anti-police
OL,17,Fsentiment in the area.
OL,19,FHundreds of people went on to loot
OL,20,Fshops, vandalise buildings and pelt
OL,21,Fbricks at emergency services.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/20
