OL,6,FViolence had also spread from North
OL,7,FTyneside to Newcastle - with business
OL,8,Fand homes in the West End also
OL,9,Ftargeted.
OL,11,FThe Asian communities living in Meadow
OL,12,FWell had also been caught up in the
OL,13,Ffiring line, with hundreds of
OL,14,Fprotestors shouting racist slogans.
OL,16,FPasha's shop was nearby to the Meadow
OL,17,FWell area.
OL,19,FHe said: " People were saying that if
OL,20,Fyou weren't the same colour of skin,
OL,21,Fthey will hit you.
