OL,6,FIn 1992 he said: "86% unemployment and
OL,7,Fa neglect by local and central
OL,8,FGovernment ensured an anonymity of
OL,9,Fpoverty that permeates every brick.
OL,11,F"The local library closes in the early
OL,12,Fsummer of 1991, 25% of the estates'
OL,13,Fhouses are boarded up and 80% of
OL,14,Finhabited houses require repairs," he
