OL,6,FDespite everything that has happened,
OL,7,Fthere is a hope within the community
OL,8,Fthat things will get better.
OL,10,F"I'm a Mackem as much as anyone else
OL,11,Fis in Sunderland. I've seen a lot of
OL,12,Fpeople, and we do get along, it's just
OL,13,Fsmall individuals that don't
OL,14,Funderstand you know. It's 2024 now.
OL,16,F"I do hope for the best that we do
OL,17,Fhave the communities, get together,
